    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;evocation&nbsp;[fire];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Wizard 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect:</strong>&nbsp;One or more rays\n<br>\n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;Instantaneous\n<br>\n    \n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;None\n\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\nYou blast your enemies with fiery rays. You may fire one ray, plus one additional ray for every four levels beyond 3rd (to a maximum of three rays at 11th level). Each ray requires a ranged touch attack to hit and deals 4d6 points of fire damage.\n</p><p>The rays may be fired at the same or different targets, but all bolts must be aimed at targets within 30 feet of each other and fired simultaneously.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
